Risk Table (Probability/Impact/Response)

 Risk Register

| Risk Category | Risk Description | Probability | Impact | Response |
|---------------|-----------------|-------------|--------|----------|
| Technical | API outage stops live price updates | High | High | Add fallback data cache |
| Technical | Data loss during CSV import/export | Medium | High | Validate input before save |
| Technical | Login system security vulnerability | Medium | High | Enforce stronger passwords |
| Schedule | Sprint tasks take longer than expected | High | Medium | Break work into smaller tasks |
| Schedule | Delays in testing features before release | Medium | High | Add buffer days |
| Schedule | Missed deadlines from team workload | Low | High | Adjust timeline with sponsor |
| Financial | Cloud hosting cost higher than expected | Medium | Medium | Track usage, set alerts |
| Financial | Extra expenses for software tools/licenses | Medium | Medium | Approve tools early |
| Financial | Penalty if release milestone is late | Low | High | Communicate with sponsor |
| People | Team member missing work during sprint | Medium | Medium | Cross-train members |
| People | Miscommunication between developers/testers | High | Medium | Use daily check-ins |
| People | Low team motivation slows progress | Medium | Medium | Encourage progress updates |

